      <title>就业增长乏力，澳大利亚失业率创两年新高</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australia-unemployment-hits-2-year-high-jobs-growth-sputters-2024-02-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚一月份的就业出人意料地疲弱，而失业率则攀升至两年高位，这再次表明，面对经济放缓和消费者需求疲弱，劳动力市场正在放松。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australia-unemployment-hits-2-year-high-jobs-growth-sputters-2024-02-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 00:44:28 GMT</pubDate>
